               <p>Prisoner. I am no scholar; the clerk used to go round with me to sign the receipts - then he left off<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183302140031"></xptr>going round, and used to write out a great many receipts for me.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18330214-33-verdict197" type="verdictDescription">
