               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 27. - <rs id="t18330214-33-punish198" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18330214-33-punish198" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330214-33-defend438 t18330214-33-punish198"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>MR. GRIFFITHS. I lost a great number of pigeons, some hay and corn, and was informed the prisoner carried them away; I have a number of other cases of embezzlement against him.</p>
